This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4633

Robo helps Android development by doing little things like:

Inserting missing imports,
Jumping to the manifest file,
Jumping to an activity from a list of available activities,
Adding activities (both the .java file and the entry in the manifest),
Starting an emulator.

Documentation
-------------------
In vim :h robo
or at https://bitbucket.org/ercax/robo .
